{"tid":1633771,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實大家都係對休息日衣個字反感","createTime":"2019-10-07T05:12:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T21:58:04.000Z","uid":69941,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"49b9e7679409d9a6640593c6ccdd2e784bb2ccba","tid":1633771,"uid":69941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:12:05.000Z","msg":"休息日衣個字我聽落都會覺得反感，明明緊急法都出埋仲講d咩休息日<br />\n<br />\n正題 我同意裝修係可以比到壓力政府，但長久既裝修會令人麻木，我覺得話休息日既手足其實唔係想切割，只係人權法在前，想轉用一種較平和既方法去比壓力，諗番我地前幾日十八區開花裝修，我地今日點解唔可以十八區悼念走左既手足，裝飾同唱歌<br />\n<br />\n所以唔好再用休息日衣個字喇 今晚我地十八區開花裝飾，唱歌啦  最後和理非同勇武都請你地記住 要贏衣場運動 冇一邊可以分割<br />\n 光復香港 時代革命 <br />\n講野1999 sorry"},{"pid":"aee7f71fb14a9476bebdfcb7ee4f685b925610cb","tid":1633771,"uid":69941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:12:15.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"ac88b5ab6dbd99ab2c1e4a13713ecb1c1b9e6228","tid":1633771,"uid":69941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:12:32.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"d60fa5a721854ca9facdda209889119a201b0959","tid":1633771,"uid":69941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:12:43.000Z","msg":"推3"},{"pid":"06aae1f9c9de4dd662c51dca63842cac8942916d","tid":1633771,"uid":42549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:12:53.000Z","msg":"香港人一定要團結<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到底邊個最想以後取消百萬大遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1633735\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1633735</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"30c5ba186fe93fafec55c484de2c34a5e74dee51","tid":1633771,"uid":69941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:12:53.000Z","msg":"推4"},{"pid":"eae4d8b680fc1970c082224f0bcf7337ea7dd088","tid":1633771,"uid":69941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:13:30.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"25209dd70409df62cbe0ace5f7c00d18b6b532f8","tid":1633771,"uid":167011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:13:39.000Z","msg":"罷工係對個政權最撚有衝擊既抗爭手法，但三罷做左咁撚多次，都係得8.5成功，因為計劃左好撚耐，對香港人黎講，個個都只想被罷工，到呢個地步，你仲想做休息撚，而唔乘勝追擊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n勿拆黨鐵！！全民被罷工！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1633581\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1633581</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n三樣香港人應同樣憎恨既野：<br />\n政府、黑警、黨鐵<br />\n<br />\n呢三樣先係主線<br />\n你個啲乜鳩紅藍店，我理撚得你幾時搞？<br />\n個啲要休息，冇問題，但咁撚樣都唔食住上，令到全港自動罷工，咁我真係代表我全力支持既香港政府多謝你為香港既經濟服務<br />\n<br />\n唔撚係話和理非冇用，但勇和齊上齊落，兩邊一齊做唔撚得？"},{"pid":"0bc2fb3e890fe2f8500fbc50530d4592119d091b","tid":1633771,"uid":69941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:13:55.000Z","msg":"7/10"},{"pid":"b7ccd8a09512cb1d12ace603a3f0fef39ba318f7","tid":1633771,"uid":69941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:14:05.000Z","msg":"今晚見啦"},{"pid":"e3928d5b895d7b686677e8360db3a72418ecb51d","tid":1633771,"uid":262043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:15:06.000Z","msg":"有一班人認為美國唔會因為示威示暴力而叫停法案<br />\n其實依個情況同當初修例一樣<br />\n信則有 不信則無 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8eff01b07bf7facef19a58d90224b670188d3caf","tid":1633771,"uid":259993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aee7f71fb14a9476bebdfcb7ee4f685b925610cb","tid":1633771,"uid":69941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:12:15.000Z","msg":"1/10"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:15:45.000Z","msg":"文宣日 連儂夜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15653a61cf02908aa02d34e4d9fa4fca52c643ec","tid":1633771,"uid":69941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:16:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/10/07/131647_ec0aab2cb0dc5f1d14e28e5f16fd2837.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?